snippet.title: Just Dance 3 | Nintendo Wii Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The world's #1 dance game brand is back with JUST DANCE 3! With over 45 new songs, new modes and new moves, JUST DANCE 3 is sure to be the best Just Dance game yet! JUST DANCE 3 is available everywhere, NOW!  ESRB Rated EVERYONE 10+ with Lyrics.

Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/justdancegame
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/justdance_game
Website: http://www.justdancegame.com
